data StringPiece = StringPiece CString CInt

instance Storable StringPiece where
    alignment _ = 8
{-# LINE 53 "Text/RE2/C.hsc" #-}
    sizeOf    _ = (16)
{-# LINE 54 "Text/RE2/C.hsc" #-}
    peek ptr = liftM2 StringPiece
        ((\hsc_ptr -> peekByteOff hsc_ptr 0)   ptr)
{-# LINE 56 "Text/RE2/C.hsc" #-}
        ((\hsc_ptr -> peekByteOff hsc_ptr 8) ptr)
{-# LINE 57 "Text/RE2/C.hsc" #-}
    poke ptr (StringPiece dat len) = do
        (\hsc_ptr -> pokeByteOff hsc_ptr 0)   ptr dat
{-# LINE 59 "Text/RE2/C.hsc" #-}
        (\hsc_ptr -> pokeByteOff hsc_ptr 8) ptr len
{-# LINE 60 "Text/RE2/C.hsc" #-}
